title: The 'incredible story' of the British coach at Super Bowl

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: The 'incredible story' of the British coach at Super Bowl
sources.description: Aden Durde's journey to Sunday's Super Bowl is not just unusual, it's unique. The Briton's love of the NFL began with a 1986 video cassette - now he is coaching in sport's biggest game.
